Romeo Bosetti https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Romeo_Bosetti 0 Romeo Bosetti (18 January 1879 – 27 October 1948) was an Italian-born French actor and screenwriter. Bosetti was born in Romolus Joseph Bosetti Chiari, Italy and died in 1948 in Suresnes, France. Romeo_Bosetti ( 18_January_1879 – 27_October_1948 ) was an_Italian-born_French_actor_and_screenwriter .
